.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

Food: corn, plum, cucumber, blueberry, pomegranate
Birthday: march, april, january, july, december
City: rome, colone, boston, london, hannover
House: cornmaster, townhouse, cottage, futuristic, ranch-style
Job: manager, police-officer, dancer, lawyer, nurse
1. Birthday:march == Food:cucumber
2. Birthday:swedish == Job:dancer
3. Birthday:april == City:london
4. Food:plum is on the left of Food:blueberry
5. Food:plum == City:colone
6. House:cottage == Job:police-officer
7. Food:pomegranate == House:townhouse
8. City:boston is in the middle
9. Birthday:july is on the far left
10. House:ranch-style is on the left or right of Job:manager
11. Job:nurses is on the left or right of House:townhouse
12. House:cornmaster == City:rome
13. Birthday:january == House:futuristic
14. Birthday:july is on the left or right of Food:corn
15. House:ranch-style is on the left or right of City:hannover

.:: Answer ::.
